Supported Frequencies

```
2.4GHz Band:
• 2400 MHz, 2412 MHz, 2422 MHz, 2437 MHz, 2452 MHz, 2462 MHz

5GHz Band:  
• 5180 MHz, 5200 MHz, 5240 MHz, 5745 MHz

Specialty Frequencies:
• 240 MHz, 433.92 MHz
```

Detection Capabilities

· Signal Types: WiFi cameras, Bluetooth spy devices, proprietary wireless cameras
· Range: Dependent on Flipper Zero's SubGhz capabilities (typically 50-100m)
· Accuracy: High precision with frequency-specific threat assessment
· Response Time: Immediate detection with <1 second alert triggering

User Interface

Main Display

· Header: Application title and version
· Status Panel: Current scanning state and active frequency
· Threat Display: Visual threat level indicators and progress bars
· Statistics: Real-time counters for signals and scan duration
· Control Hints: Button mapping guidance

Control Scheme

· Right Button: Start/Stop scanning
· Left Button: Reset statistics and clear history
· OK Button: Alternative scan toggle
· Back Button: Safe application exit with auto-scan stop
